# Hospital Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project is an interactive Hospital Analytics Dashboard developed using Python and data visualization libraries. It provides a comprehensive view of hospital operations by analyzing patient demographics, treatment costs, diagnosis trends, department performance, and length of stay metrics.

The dashboard enables healthcare administrators and decision-makers to identify high-cost treatments, monitor departmental efficiency, understand patient distribution patterns, and uncover opportunities for improving healthcare service delivery.

## Key Features

* Patient demographic analysis by age, gender, and blood type
* Treatment cost analysis across diagnoses and departments
* Department performance monitoring
* Length of stay (LOS) analysis
* Diagnosis distribution visualization
* Identification of high-cost patients
* Interactive charts and filtering capabilities

## Insights Generated

The dashboard helps hospitals:

* Track healthcare costs and resource utilization
* Identify departments requiring operational improvements
* Monitor disease prevalence and treatment patterns
* Support data-driven decision-making
* Improve patient care and hospital efficiency

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Pandas
* NumPy
* Plotly
* Matplotlib
* Data Analytics & Visualization

## Conclusion

This dashboard demonstrates how healthcare data can be transformed into actionable insights that support operational excellence, cost management, and improved patient outcomes.
